window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>We live in the 21st Century. There is no better time to start a business than now. With the enabling power of technology, turning a great idea into a successful business does not have to be merely a dream. It can be a reality.<i>The Lemonade Stand</i> presents a new perspective on entrepreneurship that anyone who is considering starting a business or already running one, should read. <i>The Lemonade Stand</i> principles are thirteen guidelines that empower anyone to welcome adversity and transform problems into innovations. </p>"; 
